      <p>Automation can empower businesses to make better decisions, deliver better customer experiences and increase productivity. However, there are often so many opportunities for automation that companies often don't know where to start.</p>
  
      <p>DigiFi's mission is to help businesses make better automated decisions. A major component of this is providing technology that makes decision automation easy and intuitive, but we also love working closely with our customers to identify high-valueautomation opportunities and implement elegant solutions to the problem.</p>
      
      <p>With that in mind, we wanted to share a few common use cases of our platform. This list is not intended to be exhaustive, but instead to provide a few ideas. If you’d like to discuss your specific business in more detail, please contact our support team at support@digifi.io or (646) 663-3392. We look forward to hearing from you! </p>
